  <para>
    <classname>QuadSplit</classname> is a <xref
    linkend="RegisteredClass-Rationalizer"/> applied by the <xref
    linkend="RegisteredClass-Rationalize"/> &skel; <link
    linkend="RegisteredClass-SkeletonModifier">modifier</link>.  It
    splits quadrilateral &elems; into two triangular &elems;, if the
    quadrilateral has an interior angle greater than
    <varname>angle</varname>.
  </para>

  <para>
    <xref linkend="Table:ration_short"/> illustrates the triggering
    condition and the final result of the procedure. Unlike other
    rationalizers, <classname>QuadSplit</classname> doesn't affect its
    neighboring elements.
  </para>

